|0||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!39||2||2||0||2||0||0||0||43||2\n|-\n|[[York City F.C.|York City]] (loan)\n|[[2015\u201316 York City F.C. season|2015\u201316]]<ref name=sb1516/>\n|League Two\n|7||0||1||0||colspan=2|\u2014||2{{efn|name=FLT}}||0||10||0\n|-\n|[[Bengaluru FC|Bengaluru]]\n|[[2015\u201316 Bengaluru FC season|2015\u201316]]<ref name=Soccerway/>\n|[[I-League]]\n|10||0|| || ||colspan=2|\u2014||6{{efn|Appearances in [[AFC Cup]]}}||0||16||0\n|-\n|[[Leyton Orient F.C.|Leyton Orient]]\n|[[2016\u201317 Leyton Orient F.C. season|2016\u201317]]<ref name=sb1617>{{soccerbase season|40835|2016|accessdate=21 May 2017}}</ref>\n|League Two\n|30||0||0||0||colspan=2|\u2014||1{{efn|Appearance in [[EFL Trophy]]}}||0||31||0\n|-\n|[[F.C. Halifax Town]]\n|[[2017\u201318 National League#National League|2017\u201318]]<ref name=Soccerway>{{cite web |title=M. Collins: Summary |url=https://uk.soccerway.com/players/michael-collins/50966/ |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=18 May 2018}}</ref>\n|[[National League (division)|National League]]\n|22||0||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||1{{efn|Appearance in [[FA Trophy]]}}||0||23||0\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!369||23||19||3||12||1||18||1||418||28\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Managerial statistics==\n{{updated|match played 1 September 2018}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\t\t\n|+ Managerial record by team and tenure\t\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Team\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Nat\n!rowspan=\"2\"|From\n!rowspan=\"2\"|To\n!colspan=\"8\"|Record\t\n!rowspan=2|{{abbr|Ref|Reference}}\n|-\t\n!{{Tooltip|G|Games managed}}\n!{{Tooltip|W|Games won}}\n!{{Tooltip|D|Games drawn}}\n!{{Tooltip|L|Games lost}}\n!{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n!{{Tooltip|GD|Goal difference}}\n!{{Tooltip|Win %|Winning percentage}}\t\t\t\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=left|18 June 2018\n|align=left|3 September 2018\n{{WDL|7|2|1|4|for=5|against=9|diff=yes}}\t\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/teams/team.sd?team_id=234&teamTabs=results|title=2018\u201319 Bradford  Fixtures & Results|publisher=Soccerbase|accessdate=18 June 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| colspan=4 | '''Career Total'''\t\n{{WDLtot|7|2|1|4|for=5|against=9|diff=yes}}\t\n!\u2014\t\t\t\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Scunthorpe United'''\n*[[EFL League Two|Football League Two]] runner-up: [[2013\u201314 Football League Two|2013\u201314]]<ref name=Soccerway/>\n\n'''Bengaluru'''\n*[[I-League]]: [[2015\u201316 I-League|2015\u201316]]<ref name=Soccerway/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.fai.ie/ireland/player/97184 Michael Collins profile] at the Football Association of Ireland website\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Bradford City A.F.C. managers}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Collins, Michael}}\n[[Category:1986 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Halifax, West Yorkshire]]\n[[Category:Footballers from West Yorkshire]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:English expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland association footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland expatriate association footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Republic of Ireland under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Huddersfield Town A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Scunthorpe United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:AFC Wimbledon players]]\n[[Category:Oxford United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:York City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Bengaluru FC players]]\n[[Category:Leyton Orient F.C. players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Halifax Town players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:I-League players]]\n[[Category:Bradford City A.F.C. non-playing staff]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in India]]\n[[Category:English expatriate sportspeople in India]]\n[[Category:Irish expatriate sportspeople in India]]\n[[Category:English people of Irish descent]]\n[[